  "prompt": "Where is the best guitar buying shop in Guwahati?",
  "response": "Guwahati, being a major city in Assam, has several music stores where you can find a good selection of guitars. While the \"best\" shop can be subjective based on personal preferences, here are a few well-known and highly recommended guitar shops in Guwahati:\n\n1. **Furtados Music Store**  \n   Located in **GS Road, Guwahati**, Furtados is a well-known chain of music stores in India. They offer a wide range of guitars, from entry-level to premium brands, along with accessories and expert advice.\n\n2. **Melody House**  \n   Situated in **Paltan Bazaar, Guwahati**, Melody House is a popular store for musical instruments, including guitars. They have a decent collection of acoustic, electric, and bass guitars from various brands.\n\n3. **Sound of Music**  \n   Located in **Bhangagarh, Guwahati**, Sound of Music is a trusted store for guitars and other musical instruments. They offer a variety of options for beginners and professionals alike.\n\n4. **Guitar House**  \n   Found in **Beltola, Guwahati**, Guitar House is known for its friendly service and good collection of guitars. They also provide guitar lessons and maintenance services.\n\n5. **Bivek Academy of Guitars**  \n   Located in **Bharalumukh, Guwahati**, this shop is run by a renowned guitarist, Bivek Baruah. It\u2019s a great place to find quality guitars and receive expert guidance.\n\n6. **Rhythm N Groove**  \n   Situated in **Maligaon, Guwahati**, this store offers a range of guitars and accessories. The staff is knowledgeable and helpful, making it a good option for both beginners and experienced players.\n\nBefore making a purchase, it\u2019s always a good idea to visit the stores, try out the guitars, and compare prices and quality. Some stores also offer discounts or financing options, so inquire about those as well.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
